Cancer research priorities and gaps in Iran: the influence of cancer burden on 
cancer research outputs between 1997 and 2014.

Majidi A(1), Salimzadeh H(2), Beiki O(3), Delavari F(4), Majidi S(5), Delavari 
A(6), Malekzadeh R(7).

